Why?

27
00:11:04,930 --> 00:11:07,592
He was in a hurry but he still ate so much.

28
00:11:10,236 --> 00:11:11,294
Like a hungry dog.

29
00:11:24,150 --> 00:11:25,139
Can you not smoke at work?

30
00:11:25,351 --> 00:11:26,648
