Are you Thai? (Thai)
Stay there! (Cambodian)

90
00:17:53,505 --> 00:17:54,529
How are you? (Thai)

91
00:17:54,706 --> 00:17:55,900
Stay there! (Cambodian)

92
00:17:57,876 --> 00:17:58,865
Calm down! (Thai)

93
00:17:59,111 --> 00:18:00,669
Stay there! (Cambodian)

94
